<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<section name="483">
	<p>
		To find out how well your investments have done,
		<random dice="2">
			<adjust god="The Three Fortunes" amount="1"/>
			<adjust codeword="Almanac" amount="1"/>
			<adjust codeword="Bastion" amount="1"/>
			<adjust codeword="Catalyst" amount="1"/>
			<adjust codeword="Eldritch" amount="1"/>
		</random>.
		Add 1 to the score if you are an initiate of the Three Fortunes. Also add 1 for each of the following codewords that you have acquired on your travels: <i>Almanac</i>, <i>Bastion</i>, <i>Catalyst</i> and <i>Eldritch</i>.
	</p>
	<outcomes>
		<outcome range="2-3">
			<lose shards="*" cache="6.440">Lose entire sum invested</lose>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="4-5">
			<adjustmoney cache="6.440" multiply="0.5">
				Loss of 50%
			</adjustmoney>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="6-7">
			<adjustmoney cache="6.440" multiply="0.1">
				Loss of 10%
			</adjustmoney>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="8-10">Investment remains unchanged</outcome>
		<outcome range="11-12">
			<adjustmoney cache="6.440" multiply="1.1">
				Profit of 10%
			</adjustmoney>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="13-14">
			<adjustmoney cache="6.440" multiply="1.25">
				Profit of 25%
			</adjustmoney>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="15-16">
			<adjustmoney cache="6.440" multiply="1.5">
				Profit of 50%
			</adjustmoney>
		</outcome>
		<outcome range="17">
			<adjustmoney cache="6.440" multiply="2">
				Profit of 100%
			</adjustmoney>
		</outcome>
	</outcomes>
	<p>
		Now <goto section="440"/>, where you can withdraw the sum recorded in the box there after adjusting it according to the result you&#8217;ve just rolled.
	</p>
</section>
